[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:            nextEntry = [0m[1;35msupplier.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/main/java/org/apache/commons/compress/archivers/examples/Expander.jav[0m[1;92ma:303[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m309[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m303[0m[39m:    public void [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal String format, final InputStream archive, final [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath targetDirectory, final CloseableConsumer closeableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m304[0m[39m:            throws IOException, ArchiveException [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m305[0m[39m:        try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCloseableConsumerAdapter c = new [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCloseableConsumerAdapter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcloseableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m306[0m[39m:            final ArchiveInputStream<?> archiveInputStream = [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mArchiveStreamFactory.DEFAULT.createArchiveInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, archive[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m307[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mc.track[0m[1;39m([0m[39marchiveInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, targetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m308[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m309[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/main/java/org/apache/commons/compress/archivers/ArchiveEntry.jav[0m[1;92ma:75[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m84[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:    default Path [0m[1;35mresolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal Path parentPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m76[0m[39m:        final String name = [0m[1;35mgetName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m77[0m[39m:        final Path outputFile = [0m[1;35mparentPath.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m78[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35moutputFile.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparentPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mString.format[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Zip slip '%s' + '%s' -> '%s'"[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparentPath, name, outputFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:        return outputFile;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m82[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m83[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m84[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/main/java/org/apache/commons/compress/archivers/examples/Expander.jav[0m[1;92ma:69[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m70[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:        final boolean nullTarget = targetDirectory == null;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:        final Path targetDirPath = nullTarget ? null : [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtargetDirectory.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Core Insight and Root Cause  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The default `[0m[1;35mArchiveEntry.resolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparentPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` only calls [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparentPath.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and then checks the lexicographic prefix. It[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoes _not_ resolve any existing filesystem symlinks in the target directory.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If the user-supplied `targetDirectory` or one of its subpaths is or contains a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msymlink, then normalizing alone cannot prevent writes from traversing that symlink [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto an external location. The Jazzer sanitizer still sees writes outside the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintended sandbox and throws `FilePathTraversal`.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Critical Logic to Preserve  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must continue to use `resolveIn` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor equivalent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to catch “zip‐slip” via [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`..` or absolute paths.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must still create directories on demand [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Files.createDirectories`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwrite entry contents as before.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must not alter any harness or fuzzing logic. All fixes live inside [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Expander.java`’s `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` implementation.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fix Strategy: Canonicalize the Base Directory  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Before processing any entries, ensure the target directory exists on disk, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthen compute its real, symlink-resolved path once and reuse it for every entry.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Pass that canonical path to `[0m[1;35mresolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` so that the prefix check is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mperformed against the symlink-resolved base directory.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Concretely, in the `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mArchiveEntrySupplier<T>, ArchiveEntryBiConsumer<T>, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath targetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Replace  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        final boolean nullTarget = targetDirectory == null;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        final Path targetDirPath = nullTarget ? null : [0m[1;35mtargetDirectory.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      with  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        final boolean nullTarget = targetDirectory == null;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        final Path targetDirPath;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnullTarget[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            targetDirPath = null;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure the target directory exists on the filesystem[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mFiles.createDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Resolve symlinks in the target directory to obtain a canonical base[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            targetDirPath = [0m[1;35mtargetDirectory.toRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLinkOption.NOFOLLOW_LINKS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Leave the existing loop and the `[0m[1;35mresolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls intact. [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBecause `targetDirPath` is now symlink-resolved, the built-in zip-slip check [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` + `[0m[1;35mstartsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparentPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will correctly prevent any output file [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom being located outside the real directory.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Retain the `try/catch` around `[0m[1;35mresolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to skip entries that [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicitly fail the zip-slip check.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why This Works  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By normalizing **and** real‐resolving the base directory once, any filesystem [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msymlink under that base is concretely collapsed. Thus [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mparentPath.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[39mparentPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` truly enforces “no [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal outside this real directory.”  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not modify `ArchiveEntry.resolveIn` or any external library code—only [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mour own `Expander` logic.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All overloads of `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` funnel through this same method, so the fix is [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muniversal.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do not touch the fuzz harness, do not weaken exception handling, and do not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremove functionality.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigations  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If `targetDirectory` did not exist, we now always create it before expansion. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis behavior is consistent with the existing code’s directory‐creation logic for [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` fails [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., due to permission issues[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the fuzzer or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalling code will receive an `IOException` and abort. This is preferable to an [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mundetected traversal.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Minor performance cost for a single `Files.createDirectories` and `toRealPath`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall; negligible compared to per‐entry processing.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Summary  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Implement the above change** in `Expander.java` only.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This patch guarantees that any symlinks in the target directory are resolved [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mup front, closing the path‐traversal hole that remained after the previous [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnormalization‐only patch.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No other parts of the codebase, harness, or test suites need alterations.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a Jazzer-detected security finding of a file path traversal [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerability in the `Expander.expand` method of the Apache Commons Compress [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexamples. The fuzzer triggers a `FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical` exception from the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FilePathTraversal` sanitizer when attempting to extract an archive entry whose [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolved path escapes the intended output directory.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch was applied to the `Expander` class that [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m creates the target directory [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mup front, [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m resolves it to a real path using `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mNOFOLLOW_LINKS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwraps each `resolveIn` call in a try-catch to skip entries causing `IOException`, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m adjusts how the lambda-based `expand` overload is invoked.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the fuzzer still reports the same type of file path [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal exception, now pointing to a different line in `Expander.expand`.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Jazzer reports `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFile path traversal` during a fuzzing run.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer’s stack trace shows `pathFirstArgHook` being triggered on a call[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto `Files.createDirectories` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor similar file-writing API[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m in `Expander.expand`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The call stack walks through multiple overloaded `expand` methods in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Expander` example, finally reaching `ExpanderFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mFiles.newOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mwriter.accept[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextEntry, outputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:            nextEntry = [0m[1;35msupplier.get[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Centralize and canonicalize the target directory in every public API before any [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfile‐system operations:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a private helper method, e.g.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```java[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      private Path [0m[1;35mcanonicalizeTarget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath targetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory == null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              return null;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Ensure directory exists on disk[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;35mFiles.createDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Canonicalize to eliminate symlinks and normalize[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          return [0m[1;35mtargetDirectory.toRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mLinkOption.NOFOLLOW_LINKS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In *every* public `[0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` overload—whether it takes `File` or [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Path`—replace the direct use of the incoming `targetDirectory` with a call to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcanonicalizeTarget[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - For `File` parameters, call `[0m[1;35mtoPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` then `canonicalizeTarget`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - For `Path` parameters, call `canonicalizeTarget` directly.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Pass the returned canonical `Path` into the internal extraction logic only.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Eliminate any two-argument shortcuts that bypass both canonicalization and the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthree-argument expand:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove or refactor calls such as  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mc.track[0m[1;39m([0m[39marchiveInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, targetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     so that they instead invoke the canonicalize step and then call  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39msupplier, writer, canonicalTargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - For example, the `String/ InputStream/ Path/ CloseableConsumer` overload [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecomes:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public void [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString format,[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        InputStream archive,[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        Path targetDirectory,[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        CloseableConsumer closeableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         throws IOException, ArchiveException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         Path canonical = [0m[1;35mcanonicalizeTarget[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCloseableConsumerAdapter c = new [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCloseableConsumerAdapter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcloseableConsumer[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             ArchiveInputStream<?> ais = [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mArchiveStreamFactory.DEFAULT.createArchiveInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat, archive[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mc.track[0m[1;39m([0m[39mais[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m -> [0m[1;35mais.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry, out[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m -> [0m[1;35mIOUtils.copyLarge[0m[1;39m([0m[39mais, out[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 canonical[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Repeat this pattern for *all* public overloads [0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile/Path, [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mSeekableByteChannel, ZipFile, TarFile, SevenZFile, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so that every path‐based [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdispatch first calls `canonicalizeTarget`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Harden the private `<T extends ArchiveEntry> [0m[1;35mexpand[0m[1;39m([0m[39msupplier, writer, Path [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the first `[0m[1;35mFiles.createDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirectory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit is now handled[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby canonicalizeTarget[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Assume at entry that `targetDirectory` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor `targetDirPath`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is either `null` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor a canonical real path.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Retain the existing logic that wraps `[0m[1;35mnextEntry.resolveIn[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtargetDirPath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtry‐catch of `IOException` to skip entries with illegal name segments.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Since the root is now canonical, the `resolveIn` lexical check is sufficient [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto block both “..[0m[35m/[0m[39m” and symlink bypass.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Verify that no file‐system API [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `Files.createDirectories`, [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Files.newOutputStream`, `IOUtils.copyLarge`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is ever invoked on a non‐canonical [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All calls inside the private expand should use the `targetDirPath` established[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mby `canonicalizeTarget`.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This guarantees the sanitizer’s `pathFirstArgHook` sees only safe, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minside‐the‐root paths.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Regression and side‐effect considerations:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing functionality [0m[1;39m([0m[39mall overloads, null–target behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remains intact; [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly the directory path is fully normalized up‐front.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Tests or samples relying on symlinks in the extraction directory will now [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolve those symlinks rather than follow them; document this security hardening.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or fuzzing logic is altered; all fuzz entry points still invoke the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame public APIs.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Justification:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By canonicalizing the extraction root once at API boundary, all downstream [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`resolveIn` checks become reliable [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthey compare against an absolute, symlink‐free [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparent[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Removing ad‐hoc two-argument expand calls ensures no code path can bypass this[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcanonicalization.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This pattern is consistent with standard zip‐slip mitigations in the codebase [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcf. other libraries that call `toRealPath` on the output root[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Catching only `IOException` from `resolveIn` continues to skip malicious [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries without catching sanitizer exceptions [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwe do not swallow [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer will no longer see any file operation on a path that could [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mescape the intended directory, eliminating the Jazzer finding.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo external libraries, fuzz harness, or test code are modified. All changes live [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin `Expander.java`. [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
